unsql installation instructions
-----------------------------------


Content
=======

1. Package structure
2. Dependencies
3. Installation


1. Package structure
=====================

AUTHORS                 # contributors of code and patches
ChangeLog               # list of changes
COPYING                 # license
INSTALL                 # this file
Makefile                # basic makefile
README                  # user manual
TODO                    # just ideas, no plans


2. Dependencies
===============

In order to compile unsql, you need to install glibc devel package.


3. Basic installation
=====================

 1. tar xf unsql_x.x.x.tar.bz2

 2. cd unsql-x.x.x

 3. make

 4. make install
    (depending on your installation destination, you need to be root)

 5. make clean (optional)
